OL,3,CJailed groomers branded 'scum of the
OL,4,Cearth' in court by victim
OL,6,FTwo cousins who groomed vulnerable
OL,7,Fteenage girls to sexually abuse and
OL,8,Fpass around to other men were branded
OL,9,F"scum of the earth" by a victim as
OL,10,Fthey were jailed for a "campaign of
OL,11,Frape".
OL,13,FPaedophiles Manzorr Hussain, 54, and
OL,14,FImtiaz Ali, 53, both ran stalls at
OL,15,FBury market in Greater Manchester,
OL,16,Fwhere they first preyed upon the
OL,17,Fyoungsters.
