OL,3,CJailed groomers branded 'scum of the
OL,4,Cearth' in court by victim
OL,6,FBoth were convicted of multiple
OL,7,Foffences against girls, aged between
OL,8,F13 and 16, following a four-week trial
OL,9,Fearlier this year at Minshull Street
OL,10,FCrown Court in Manchester.
OL,12,FHussain, a grandfather, of Manchester
OL,13,FRoad, Bury, was jailed for 30 years
OL,14,Fafter being convicted of seven counts
OL,15,Fof rape and seven counts of indecent
OL,16,Fassault against five girls.
