OL,3,CJailed groomers branded 'scum of the
OL,4,Cearth' in court by victim
OL,6,FAli, of Ainsworth Road, Radcliffe, was
OL,7,Fjailed for 28 years after being
OL,8,Fconvicted of five counts of rape, five
OL,9,Fcounts of indecent assault and one
OL,10,Fcount of attempted indecent assault.
OL,12,FHussain waved to members of his family
OL,13,Fsat in the public dock as he was sent
OL,14,Fdown.
OL,16,FAli began abusing the girls with his
OL,17,Frelatives shortly after his arrival in
OL,18,Fthe UK from Pakistan in 1996.
