OL,6,FHussain's older brother Ghulam
OL,7,FHussain, 64, who was arrested during
OL,8,Fthe police investigation but fled the
OL,9,Fcountry, did not stand trial and is
OL,10,Fbelieved to be in Pakistan.
OL,12,FOne victim tearfully read her impact
OL,13,Fstatement from the witness box,
OL,14,Fshielded by screens from the
OL,15,Fdefendants in the dock.
OL,17,FThe woman said some men would come to
OL,18,Fher school to pick her up and she
OL,19,Fsuffered three years of rape and sex
OL,20,Fabuse from the age of 13, leading to
OL,21,F"30 years of shame".
