OL,6,FShe added: "You are nothing better
OL,7,Fthan paedophiles, rapists and scum of
OL,8,Fthe earth. You are the lowest of the
OL,9,Flow."
OL,11,FShe told the court every agency or
OL,12,Findividual who had "covered up or
OL,13,Fturned a blind eye are all complicit".
OL,15,FJailing both men, Judge Bernadette
OL,16,FBaxter told them: "You have shown not
OL,17,Fone jot of remorse or insight into
OL,18,Fyour behaviour.
