OL,6,F"You groomed, sexually abused and
OL,7,Fexploited the teen girls. Your
OL,8,Foffending can properly be described as
OL,9,Fa campaign of rape."
OL,11,FThe trial heard all five girls, now
OL,12,Fadults, were sexually abused by the
OL,13,Fbrothers and cousin in the late 1990s.
OL,14,FA sixth girl also alleged she was
OL,15,Fabused but was unable to relive her
OL,16,Fordeal in court.
