OL,4,Cearth' in court by victim
OL,6,FThe sexual abuse took place mainly in
OL,7,FBury, but also elsewhere in the region
OL,8,Fand parts of Wales, including at
OL,9,Fhouses, in vehicles, a hotel and a car
OL,10,Fdealership.
OL,12,FThe court heard girls were often given
OL,13,Fdrugs along with alcohol, then both
OL,14,FAli and Hussain would take turns to
OL,15,Frape their victim.
