OL,3,CJailed groomers branded 'scum of the
OL,4,Cearth' in court by victim
OL,6,FOne victim, a girl then aged 14 or 15,
OL,7,Fwas taken by Hussain along with
OL,8,Fanother victim to a flat in Bury,
OL,9,Fwhere he had arranged with a gang of
OL,10,Fother men to make her available for
OL,11,Fsex.
OL,13,FHussain ordered her into a bedroom,
OL,14,Fwhere there was one bed with a stained
OL,15,Fsheet on the mattress and no other
OL,16,Ffurniture.
OL,18,FOne after another six Asian men, who
OL,19,Fshe did not know, entered the room to
OL,20,Frape and sexually assault her.
