OL,6,FOne victim said she was threatened
OL,7,Fthat if she did not comply she would
OL,8,Fbe abandoned naked on the moors above
OL,9,FBury.
OL,11,FA number of the girls were
OL,12,Fparticularly vulnerable, already
OL,13,Fhaving difficult home lives and
OL,14,Ftroubled backgrounds.
OL,16,FThe men took advantage, grooming them
OL,17,Fwith attention, showering them with
OL,18,Fgifts of drink and drugs, and
OL,19,Fsometimes a place to spend time the
OL,20,Ftrial heard.
